video.title: Jane The Virgin
video.synopsis: After vowing to remain chaste until marriage, Jane Villanueva learns she's pregnant due to a medical slip-up and has to rethink her future.

episodes.synopsis: The life of a pious, hardworking Latina woman is turned upside down when a doctor visit reveals she was artificially inseminated by accident.
episodes.title: Chapter One: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: When her baby daddy's wild past comes to light, Jane chooses to keep working in the hotel he manages to see if he and his wife would be good parents.
episodes.title: Chapter Two

episodes.synopsis: Jane decides there is no point in clinging to her virginity and plans a romantic encounter with Michael, despite her budding feelings for Rafael.
episodes.title: Chapter Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane's plan to squelch her feelings for Rafael backfires. Xo risks her relationship with her daughter by revealing the truth about Jane's father.
episodes.title: Chapter Four

episodes.synopsis: Jane finds herself in a pickle when Michael vows his loyalty and Rafael comes clean about his plans for the baby. Jane decides to get to know her dad.
episodes.title: Chapter Five

episodes.synopsis: Jane drifts away from Michael and toward Rafael. As she gets closer to her father, she must cope with his nasty stepdaughters, who attend her school.
episodes.title: Chapter Six

episodes.synopsis: Jane's electrifying kiss with Rafael prompts her to be a bit more reckless. Petra plots to take down Rafael. Xo and Rogelio end up on a double date.
episodes.title: Chapter Seven

episodes.synopsis: Rafael returns worse for the wear after an unsuccessful search for his missing sister, and Jane must decide whether to continue with the relationship.
episodes.title: Chapter Eight

episodes.synopsis: A sonogram appointment offers a window into Jane and Rafael's different philosophies on parenting. Petra makes a play for the baby.
episodes.title: Chapter Nine

episodes.synopsis: A hurricane causes a lockdown at the hotel, where a reinstated Rafael is forced to make cuts that put Jane in a bind. Alba suffers serious injuries.
episodes.title: Chapter Ten

episodes.synopsis: Jane must decide between taking a permanent teaching position at the school and accepting a writing internship at Rogelio's telenovela.
episodes.title: Chapter Eleven

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Rafael struggle to deal with various challenges from Luisa and Petra. Meanwhile, Jane gets a big break that may be too good to be true.
episodes.title: Chapter Twelve

episodes.synopsis: A pregnancy checkup takes an unexpected turn, forcing Jane to make a difficult choice and casting a shadow over her graduation.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirteen

episodes.synopsis: With Emilio still missing and the amnio results not expected for another week, Jane and Rafael try to go about their normal lives.
episodes.title: Chapter Fourteen

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Rafael revisit the issue of moving in together. Meanwhile, Jane learns that her literary idol is staying at the Marbella.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifteen

episodes.synopsis: While enjoying Miami's annual Carnaval, Jane and Rafael try to navigate the changing course of their relationship. Jane alienates her writing group.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixteen

episodes.synopsis: Daunted by impending motherhood, Jane rejects Xo's advice and worries about Rafael's fathering skills, especially when he reacts to a work crisis.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventeen

episodes.synopsis: Jane harbors doubts about Rafael and their future but sacrifices to help him at work. Rafael's estranged mother reveals a heartbreaking secret.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighteen

episodes.synopsis: When Rafael suddenly withdraws from Jane, she fights to save their troubled romance. Meanwhile, they must play the happy couple at their baby shower.
episodes.title: Chapter Nineteen

episodes.synopsis: In the aftermath of the breakup, Jane tries to focus on what is best for the baby and figure out how to co-parent with the man who broke her heart.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty

episodes.synopsis: Jane grapples with her choice to seek sole custody of her child. Her school reunion highlights the gap between the future she envisioned and her life.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-One

episodes.synopsis: Jane must set all issues aside, from her mother's absence to grad school applications to man problems, because the arrival of her baby is at hand.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Two

episodes.synopsis: Rogelio turns a frantic ordeal involving Mateo into a media circus. Jane questions her maternal instincts. Rafael seeks parenting advice from Michael.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Three

episodes.synopsis: Torn between Michael and Rafael, Jane finds herself in her own personal version of “The Bachelorette.” Xo and Rogelio perform on a cruise ship.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Jane tries to balance motherhood with her academic goals. Michael makes the mistake of taking romantic advice from Rogelio.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Five

episodes.synopsis: Jane forgets to plan Lina’s birthday party and tries to make it up to her. Meanwhile, Rafael makes a case for joint custody.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Six

episodes.synopsis: As Alba hits a surprising snag in her attempt to apply for citizenship, Rogelio has a run-in with his old friend Britney Spears.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: Jane struggles with grad school, causing her to miss big milestones in Mateo’s life. Meanwhile, Michael receives a shocking offer.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: In the midst of mulling over babysitter options for Mateo, Jane pauses for a Black Friday shopping trip and has a perplexing encounter with Michael.
episodes.title: Chapter Twenty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Jane gets creative to pay her own way for grad school. Petra finds that helping Magda with her sordid affairs may be more trouble than it’s worth.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty

episodes.synopsis: While Rogelio learns something he never knew about his father, Rafael discovers an even more shocking truth regarding his mother.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-One

episodes.synopsis: Jane learns that babies, orange juice and hard drives filled with hard work don’t mix. She also learns that dating new men is a possibility.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Two

episodes.synopsis: Awkwardness follows when it seems like Jane might be misreading Professor Chavez’s signals. Meanwhile, Rafael and Petra get closer.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane wonders if she should go further with Professor Chavez. Michael realizes he has information he can’t keep from Jane.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Four

episodes.synopsis: After confessions are made, Michael and Rafael don’t exactly play nice together. Meanwhile, Rogelio’s new assistant is a little too into him.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Five

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Petra discover the real reason behind Rafael’s concerning behavior, but the latter suddenly has more pressing matters to attend to.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Six

episodes.synopsis: While trying to win over Michael’s parents, Jane grows concerned about Rogelio’s whereabouts. Rafael finds the person he’s looking for.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: A flood disrupts Jane and Michael’s big plans. Rafael objects to the idea of Jane moving. Petra struggles with postpartum depression.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: Xo makes Jane’s bachelorette party a little more interesting than intended. Rafael tries to dig deeper into Derek’s story.
episodes.title: Chapter Thirty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Baby Mateo utters a certain word, inadvertently opening a can of worms. Jane isn’t thrilled with Xo’s questionable romantic encounter.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty

episodes.synopsis: Jane asks for extra shifts after a startling setback. Xo auditions for the telenovela. Behind the scenes, Rogelio and Dina get complicated.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-One

episodes.synopsis: A Mother’s Day tradition turns into a calamitous brunch with Petra and Anezka. Rogelio enlists Jane to help him seem smart at a fancy dinner party.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Two

episodes.synopsis: As the universe seems determined to unravel plans for Mateo’s birthday party, Jane’s writing gives Michael a strong hunch about Mutter.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane is torn between perfecting her thesis and committing to her wedding date. Michael’s partner has some new info on the case.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Michael fights for his life in the hospital. When the police ask "Petra" for help, they notice she's behaving oddly. Xo makes a confession to Rogelio.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Five

episodes.synopsis: Rafael admits something to Jane that strains their parenting relationship. Alba learns Xo's secret. Anezka looks for dirt on Rafael but finds romance.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Six

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Michael take the next step in their relationship. Rogelio makes a move to become a crossover star. Luisa chooses between her family and Rose.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: A nasty surprise ruins Jane and Michael's plans for a housewarming party. Xo starts a new career. Blackmail spurs Anezka to sell her Marbella shares.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: Rafael grows suspicious of "Petra" and begins spying on her. Alba agrees to allow Jane to read letters from Cecilia, but under one condition.
episodes.title: Chapter Forty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Jane receives an unexpected visitor. After being served with a lawsuit, Petra seeks help from Rafael. The police get a break in the Mutter case.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty

episodes.synopsis: Jane's visitor overstays her welcome. Rogelio seeks the help of a celebrity matchmaker. Rafael's childhood memories provide a clue in the Mutter case.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-One

episodes.synopsis: Michael makes a bold career change. The Villanuevas learn about Rogelio's baby plans. Petra suspects Rafael and Scott are conspiring against her.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Two

episodes.synopsis: As Jane finishes her novel and Michael preps for entrance exams, stress takes a toll. To destroy Rafael's will addendum, Petra employs a distraction.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane lands an interview for a seemingly perfect job. At his film premiere, Rogelio gets a nasty surprise. A new love interest enters Luisa's life.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Three years have passed. Mateo, now 4, has behavioral issues, Rogelio and Darci have a reality show, and Rafael is back home and has a new girlfriend.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Five

episodes.synopsis: A book deal leads Jane to consider quitting her hated job. Xo discovers Rogelio has been lying to everyone. A grisly find threatens the hotel's image.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Six

episodes.synopsis: Jane meets her surprising new editor. Abbey suggests to Rafael that they move in together. Petra hides a new relationship -- and another secret.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: Jane runs against Petra to become "room mom" at Mateo's preschool. Alba tries to impress her crush. Rogelio uses Mateo to get intel on Xo and Bruce.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: Jane decides to get back into the dating game. Alba tries to be an independent woman around Jorge. Petra learns Chuck has been talking to the police.
episodes.title: Chapter Fifty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Jane resists discussing her past to boost sales of her book. A younger male co-star makes Rogelio suspicious. Luisa and her girlfriend visit Rafael.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty

episodes.synopsis: Jane's date helps her smooth things over with Lina. Rafael decides to come clean with Petra. Xo blows off Rogelio, who's shocked when he learns why.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-One

episodes.synopsis: Jane meets Fabian's grandmother. Petra makes an interesting discovery about Chuck. Mateo starts asking difficult questions about his family's origins.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Two

episodes.synopsis: Jane finds it difficult to ask Fabian for a favor, and gets in over her head when she volunteers to help her mom and dad with their preparations.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane finds out about a letter Michael wrote. Stunning news threatens to upset Rogelio and Xo's big plans. Petra doubts Jane's feelings for Rafael.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Jane goes on a romantic walk down memory lane. Rafael launches a plan to recoup his loss. To Darci's delight, Rogelio makes a social media misstep.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Five

episodes.synopsis: A job offer forces Jane and Adam to make a decision. Rogelio and Fabian compete to impress a focus group that will decide which of their roles to cut.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Six

episodes.synopsis: When Mateo catches his mom with Adam, Jane must introduce the two sooner than she'd planned. Darci decides to have a home birth, to Rogelio's dismay.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: Jane struggles to dissuade Rafael from signing the hotel deal with Katherine. Rogelio and Darci have a hard time choosing a name for the baby.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: Adam drops a bombshell. Uncertain her fiancé is Mr. Right, Lina begs Jane for her opinion. Rafael learns his sister is experiencing hallucinations.
episodes.title: Chapter Sixty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Rival Fabian tries to thwart Rogelio's efforts to give Jane the book launch party of her dreams. Petra gives her mother a taste of her own medicine.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy

episodes.synopsis: When Jane hits the road on her book tour, Xo and Alba tag along to support her, but at her first reading, the Q&A session triggers a meltdown.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-One

episodes.synopsis: A surprise kiss elicits mixed reactions. A lie to get Mateo into a new school becomes hard to hide. Therapy leads Rogelio and Xo to breakthroughs.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Two

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Rafael feel pressured to define their relationship after recent developments confuse Mateo. Rogelio starts his new job as a stay-at-home dad.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Three

episodes.synopsis: Rogelio sparks a heated argument on a talk show when he claims he has postpartum depression. Jane helps Alba to get in touch with her sexy side.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Four

episodes.synopsis: A search for a temporary teaching job reunites Jane with an old flame. Rogelio tries to sign Eva Longoria as his new co-star instead of River Fields.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Five

episodes.synopsis: Jane wrestles with her inner critic. Rafael gets a lead on his birth mother's identity. Rogelio's efforts to be more supportive of Xo backfire.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Six

episodes.synopsis: As the family awaits medical test results, Rogelio tries to get River Fields to join his show. Mateo learns about the tooth fairy. Rafael finds Luisa.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Seven

episodes.synopsis: As Xo agonizes over a highly personal decision, Jane can't help making her own wishes known.  Petra seeks Rafael's advice on how to woo J.R.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Eight

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Rafael reach a relationship milestone, as do J.R. and Petra. Rogelio tries to poach a celeb's nanny. Alba crams for her U.S. citizenship test.
episodes.title: Chapter Seventy-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Complications arise when Rafael moves back into Alba's home to save money. Xo gets a wake-up call after making a new friend during her treatments.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty

episodes.synopsis: A U.S. citizenship party for Alba suddenly becomes two celebrations in one. Rose reveals a shocker to Rafael that could ruin his relationship with Jane.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-One

episodes.synopsis: A stunning turn of events reunites Jane with someone who is nothing like she remembers. J.R. sees another side of Petra that she refuses to tolerate.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Two

episodes.synopsis: A memory-jogging activity with Jason sends Jane into a panic. Rogelio starts filming "The Passions of Steve & Brenda" with River Fields.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Three

episodes.synopsis: To get Jason to sign the papers, Jane must go on a date with him. River Fields asks Xo to break some bad news to Rogelio. After a shock, Mateo acts out.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Four

episodes.synopsis: Jane realizes Jason's memory has returned. Facing an impossible decision, she unwisely chooses to "drink and decide." Xo celebrates her last treatment.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Five

episodes.synopsis: When life goes from bad to worse, Jane takes advice on getting past her writer's block. Rogelio discovers Baby is more attached to Esteban than him.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Six

episodes.synopsis: When Mateo asks Jane what drugs are, she begins to worry about Rafael. Xo tries to get her groove back. Alba reveals her feelings to Jorge.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Seven

episodes.synopsis: Jane's trip to Montana gets off to a rough start, but she soon finds herself getting a crash course in ranch life, and comes to a realization.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Eight

episodes.synopsis: A problem Mateo is having at school allows Jane to spend time strategizing with Rafael. Alba and Jorge rehearse for their upcoming INS interview.
episodes.title: Chapter Eighty-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Jane discovers her father and her book editor have been keeping a secret from her. Alba's flower metaphor for virginal purity comes back to haunt her.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety

episodes.synopsis: Mateo's teacher recommends he be tested to see if an underlying condition is interfering with his learning. J.R. goes to her interview in Houston.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-One

episodes.synopsis: Jane implements a plan to treat Mateo's ADHD without meds. Jorge moves into the Villanueva home. Xo anxiously awaits the results of her final PET scan.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Two

episodes.synopsis: Mateo's ADHD jeopardizes his part in a school musical. Rogelio suspects River Fields is trying to kill him. Jane meets the woman Rafael is dating.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Three

episodes.synopsis: Jane and Rafael deliver happy news to Mateo, who reacts unexpectedly. At a crossroads in her life, Xo puts her fate in the hands of an old board game.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Four

episodes.synopsis: Jane is reunited with her old friend Lina, who asks for a very big favor. Rafael's friendship with celebrity chef Ludo Lefebvre piques Petra's interest.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Five

episodes.synopsis: Rogelio's pilot is put before a test audience. Jane practices being a stepmom, and tries to find an agent to represent her newly finished second novel.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Six

episodes.synopsis: A plot twist suggested by her new agent leads Jane to reexamine an event from Mateo's infancy. Rogelio must help River Fields win her daughter back.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Seven

episodes.synopsis: While trying to shake off a bad feeling about Rose, Jane learns she must get Michael's life-story rights in order to include him in her novel.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Eight

episodes.synopsis: "Jane the Virgin" cast members reflect on the experiences and favorite moments they had while playing their characters during the show's five seasons.
episodes.title: Chapter Ninety-Nine

episodes.synopsis: Xo gets cold feet about moving to New York. Info surfaces about Rafael's birth parents. A last-minute romantic gesture complicates Jane's big day.
episodes.title: Chapter One Hundred
